rrier2" url="https://digital.slub-dresden.de/data/kitodo/AWvS_DE-1a-34292_Bd.15/AWvS_DE-1a-34292_Bd.15_tif/jpegs/00000039.tif.original.jpg"/><graphic n="4" decls="carrier2" url="https://digital.slub-dresden.de/data/kitodo/AWvS_DE-1a-34292_Bd.15/AWvS_DE-1a-34292_Bd.15_tif/jpegs/00000040.tif.original.jpg"/></facsimile><text><body><div><p><hi rend="family:Courier"><milestone unit="start" n="26997"/>[1]</hi><note type="Notiz_zur_Transkription"><title>Paginierung des Editors</title></note><milestone unit="end" n="26997"/><hi rend="family:Courier"> <placeName key="292">Cadogan Place</placeName> 27 June 1826<lb/>My Dear Sir<lb/>I am encouraged by Experience of your Kindness to ask Advice &amp; Aid from You relative to the following Project.<lb/>I am advised to try the Effort of a Journey to Switzerland &amp; </hi><hi rend="family:Courier;offset:4">of </hi><hi rend="family:Courier">some Stay there for Health.. I am advised for that Object to go by Water as much as possible – <lb/>With this View I sh</hi><hi rend="family:Courier;offset:4">d</hi><hi rend="family:Courier"> go to <placeName key="5137">Rotterdam</placeName> by Steam &amp; after showing Holland to <persName key="12918"><persName key="12919">my Family</persName></persName> endeavour to catch at <placeName key="8800">Nimeguen</placeName> the Steam Boat to <placeName key="172">Cologne</placeName>. There my Questions to You begin.<lb/>Could I hire a good Boat with suffi<milestone unit="start" n="26998"/>[2]</hi><note type="Notiz_zur_Transkription"><title>Paginierung des Editors</title></note><milestone unit="end" n="26998"/><hi rend="family:Courier">cient Means of Protection against Sun &amp; Rain from </hi><placeName key="172"><hi rend="family:Courier">Cologne</hi></placeName><hi rend="family:Courier"> to </hi><placeName key="897"><hi rend="family:Courier">Ments</hi></placeName><hi rend="family:Courier"> or </hi><placeName key="988"><hi rend="family:Courier">Mannheim</hi></placeName><hi rend="family:Courier"> – For what Sum in English Money &amp; in how many Days? Can You procure me Answers to the same Questions from Ments or Mannheim to </hi><placeName key="392"><hi rend="family:Courier">Basle</hi></placeName><hi rend="family:Courier"> or </hi><placeName key="251"><hi rend="family:Courier">Schaffhausen</hi></placeName><hi rend="family:Courier">.<lb/>I should like to see &amp; show <placeName key="574">Heidelberg</placeName> <placeName key="3175">Worms</placeName>, <placeName key="2349">Speier</placeName> <placeName key="440">Strasburg</placeName> &amp;nd or any thing </hi><hi rend="family:Courier;offset:4">else</hi><hi rend="family:Courier"> not requiring much Time Land Journey or Expense –<lb/>What is the Distance from <placeName key="392">Basle</placeName> to <placeName key="228">Coppett</placeName>? – &amp; from <placeName key="251">Schaffhausen</placeName> by <placeName key="227">Zurich</placeName> the Right </hi><placeName key="233"><hi rend="family:Courier;offset:4">Lucern</hi></placeName><hi rend="family:Courier"> &amp; <placeName key="226">Berne</placeName> <milestone unit="start" n="26999"/>[3]</hi><note type="Notiz_zur_Transkription"><title>Paginierung des Editors</title></note><milestone unit="end" n="26999"/><hi rend="family:Courier"> to Coppett<lb/>My Decision would much depend on the most worthy Information which I should receive about Time Expense &amp; Fatigue, My Party might consist only of <persName key="12918">Ly M</persName> &amp; <persName key="12919">my Daughter</persName> – or it might contain 2 perhaps 3 more – in both Cases 1 male probably 1 female servant such Estimates </hi><hi rend="family:Courier;offset:4">of Expense</hi><hi rend="family:Courier"> as you can form on probable Conjecture for economical English Travellers would be very acceptable – From the first Point in Switz whether <placeName key="392">Basle</placeName> or <milestone unit="start" n="27000"/>[4]</hi><note type="Notiz_zur_Transkription"><title>Paginierung des Editors</title></note><milestone unit="end" n="27000"/><hi rend="family:Courier"> <placeName key="251">Schaffhausen</placeName> where Water Conveyance must end My Health w</hi><hi rend="family:Courier;offset:4">d</hi><hi rend="family:Courier"> require slow Journies not exceeding 25 English Miles a day which is I suppose about the Rate of a Voiturier: A speedy Answer will much increase the Value of the Information. I write about nothing else because I hope to see you at <placeName key="887">Bonn</placeName> – <lb/>I am My Dear M</hi><hi rend="family:Courier;offset:4">r</hi><hi rend="family:Courier"> Schlegel<lb/>Yours ever most truly<lb/>Mackintosh<lb/><milestone unit="start" n="27001"/>[1]</hi><note type="Notiz_zur_Transkription"><title>Paginierung des Editors</title></note><milestone unit="end" n="27001"/><hi rend="family:Courier"> <milestone unit="start" n="27002"/>répondu le 8 Juillet</hi><note type="Notiz_zur_Transkription"><title>Notiz des Empfängers</title></note><milestone unit="end" n="27002"/><hi rend="family:Courier"></hi></p></div></body></text></TEI>
